726877f-b.title: Queens: Hollis Avenue - Jamaica Avenue
726877f-b.text:
Hollis Avenue, west side, south of Jamaica Avenue, show-
ing the old Hollis District Schoolhouse No. 2, from 1860 to
1890. Henry Miller's bicycle repair shop was here in the 192O's
and early '30's.
Views 1,2:  Eugene L. Armbruster Collection View 1: 1923
MAY BE REPRODUCED  View 2: 1925
View 3: P. L. Sperr  March 25, 1932
NO REPRODUCTIONS
